      <title>罗氏疯狂收购后，肥胖药物投资者获得了意外之财</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/obesity-drug-investors-hit-pay-dirt-as-roche-buys-into-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Carmot Therapeutics Inc. 5 月份估值为 12.5 亿美元。半年后，由于肥胖药物的疯狂需求，该公司以两倍多的价格向瑞士制药商罗氏控股公司出售产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/obesity-drug-investors-hit-pay-dirt-as-roche-buys-into-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 13:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
